# Channel

JOIN #channel ----> OK
PART #channel ----> OK (1 or more channels)
KICK user (OP)----> OK
KICK #channel user -> OK (if not operator = ERROR)

# INVITE ---> ok

PRIVMSG #channel :hello --> OK
PRIVMSG user2 :hello    --> OK
NOTICE unknown_user :hii --> OK (Expected behavoir: NO ERROR MSG)

# MODE

Mode +i                 --> OK
Mode +k                 --> OK
Mode +o                 --> OK
Mode +l                 --> OK
Mode +t                 --> OK

# Operator
if operator leaves channel , next user joins is the operator (Correct behavior is: no one becomes operator)

